	* mono/os/win32/util.c: 
	* mono/os/unix/util.c: 
	* mono/os/util.h: mono_set_rootdir() doesnt take any args now.
	(It doesn't do anything on unix builds, and the w32 version no
	longer needs an arg.)

	* configure.in: Add HOST_CC for w32 builds

